$ZAGG IMO the question isn't how well will Zagg do this quarter. It is when will announcements (or at least rumors) of new devices and new form factors start percolating in the news.  ZAGG makes cases, screens and accessories and is well positioned for the next big cycle.  If there is a killer device, the move will be quick. Sooner or later, there will be a push for 5G and/or AR devices.   Just my opinion.
